# Railway Environment Variables Configuration
# Copy these variables to your Railway project dashboard
# Go to: Project Settings → Variables

# ============================================
# DATABASE VARIABLES (Reference from PostgreSQL Service)
# ============================================
# In Railway, add these as "Reference Variables" from your PostgreSQL service:
# 1. Click "New Variable" → "Add Reference"
# 2. Select your PostgreSQL service
# 3. Map as follows:

DB_HOST=${PGHOST}
DB_PORT=${PGPORT}
DB_NAME=${PGDATABASE}
DB_USER=${PGUSER}
DB_PASS=${PGPASSWORD}

# Note: Railway automatically provides DATABASE_URL
# DATABASE_URL is auto-generated: postgresql://$PGUSER:$PGPASSWORD@$PGHOST:$PGPORT/$PGDATABASE

